{"tid":2283294,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"南韓電競選手稱「死了的中國人才是好中國人」 終被罰 2.8 萬港元","createTime":"2020-11-12T12:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T13:10:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":133,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"02ad20f7f867149e0768c70231dbe1bf81ff00ee","tid":2283294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"打機有時未必可稱心如意，也許好些玩家都會怒罵對手或隊友，不過如果是電競選手，便有可能要為自己的言行負責。Riot Games 韓國分公司今日公告，韓國 LCK 賽區戰隊 SANDBOX Gaming 打野選手金長謙（遊戲 ID：OnFleek），在單排練習時因說了「死了的中國人才是好中國人」，被指是種族歧視，將會被罰款及停賽。<br />\n<br />\n事件於 11 月 6 日發生，OnFleek 在某一場對局中，遊戲進程不如預期，之後檢舉組隊隊友打了一句，大意為「死了的中國人才是好中國人」，而且當時還在進行直播（現時直播存檔已刪除），觀眾自然也可看到這句話。至於 OnFleek 的隊伍的確有兩名中國人，分別是Vici Gaming（VG）的中路選手 Forge，以及Team WE Academy（WE.A）的輔助選手 Zhuo。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨後 Riot Games 檢視了事件，指 OnFleek 確認使用了不當語言，選手本人也承認是事實，有違他職業選手的身份。Riot Games 稱考慮到問題嚴重性，決定依據相關罰則，處以禁賽 3 場與 100 萬韓圜（約 7000 港元）罰款。<br />\n<br />\nSANDBOX Gaming 也在官方 Twitter 發表公告，對於旗下戰隊選手 OnFleek  在個人直播中做出了不當行為，造成許多粉絲的不滿與失望，深表歉意，同步刊登了 OnFleek 親筆道歉函。SB 戰隊同時決定加重處罰，除了禁止他在 2021 年 LCK 春季賽中第一輪循環賽出賽外，同時罰款提高到 300 萬韓圜（約 2.1 萬港元），並且要做 30 小時社區服務。"},{"pid":"bcd4c8e049da31eb136307317ec15b943de96a46","tid":2283294,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:37:50.000Z","msg":"OnFleek 則就自己不當言論手寫道歉信向大眾道歉，表示自己在「完全不知道隊友身分」的狀況下，使用種族歧視的語句檢舉隊友，畫面還在直播中流出，這是非常無知和不負責任的行為，在此真心道歉並進行深刻反省。"},{"pid":"cdfa232c7d8f8115f7e7461fa352bd6e125544d0","tid":2283294,"uid":108133,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:43:02.000Z","msg":"中國人同哥布林一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951abbc8a14ebf150e5a808f36bd8a058504cc7d","tid":2283294,"uid":2300,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"有咩錯，支那豬死多d 最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98130ea7803fac9b7fbd0f8751c2c08fc7ba7f94","tid":2283294,"uid":371467,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:48:12.000Z","msg":"Remember, a good chinese is a dead chinese<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d277c1925cbff40c194debbbd15cefdfc961021","tid":2283294,"uid":63253,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"一語中的"},{"pid":"21ba1fd13715c50323653ece58a66383d32aa2c8","tid":2283294,"uid":327421,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:49:46.000Z","msg":"I think he is correct."},{"pid":"e083772a52b210d4ee6fc56177f69d59568b643f","tid":2283294,"uid":303650,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:50:43.000Z","msg":"支持韓仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4468dd797f318707e7b13f4804cf80c9ce8eebe4","tid":2283294,"uid":79893,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:51:08.000Z","msg":"芝麻仁無磨菇<br />\n南韓選手無講錯喎"},{"pid":"7e0e8a56d51906a607c34745048942e15a9639ce","tid":2283294,"uid":289292,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:52:35.000Z","msg":"其實咁講又真係好過份，一竹篙打一船人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDLLM邊個話死咗既一定係好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ab7608108d17170c4ad34328e1b3fa4990fc11","tid":2283294,"uid":290393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"951abbc8a14ebf150e5a808f36bd8a058504cc7d","tid":2283294,"uid":2300,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"有咩錯，支那豬死多d 最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"賺緊中國錢, 唔方便比選手講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e88a9a74fa960b23d3ffccf3e645ae5266adfa1","tid":2283294,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbbf553cd31a31193cde365a3e521f4d984dec4","tid":2283294,"uid":1997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:56:45.000Z","msg":"中肯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1d13fe1d12920e4b4b86329566e66ca6b82ce7","tid":2283294,"uid":86395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:56:54.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f02c4fab45d87585dd6cffc4551bda341f63cf7","tid":2283294,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e66cc27831331b09c35d5aab2711edf1b85245","tid":2283294,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:57:38.000Z","msg":"客觀，中肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a76837bf6834a2e1f2a0ad6a013212b899757f5","tid":2283294,"uid":48609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"做埋肥料先叫好"},{"pid":"1cd2dd13303ce0fcd63a46734077aae24011dba8","tid":2283294,"uid":293257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:57:52.000Z","msg":"眾籌幫佢俾都得啦"},{"pid":"a912a1d465c01f89eb294b646a526443fbbeb77a","tid":2283294,"u